      "body" : "A comment, when I supply -rescan with Qt we can click the splashscreen and it fades (as it's an own thread now)... this will result in a tray-icon but NO further user feedback during re-scan. Perhaps it should show the progress via tray pop-up also?\r\n\r\nBtw. is there a RPC command to trigger a rescan during normal Qt runtime?",
